      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "terraform fmt\nterraform validate\nterraform plan -var-file=\"envs/production.tfvars\"\nterraform apply -var-file=\"envs/production.tfvars\"\n\naws eks update-kubeconfig --name dvn-workshop-production --region us-\neast-1\nkubectl get nodes\nkubectl get pods -n argocd\nkubectl get application dvn-workshop -n argocd\n\nGitOps: push em main -> CI/CD -> ECR -> kustomization.yaml -> ArgoCD\nsync",
      "fontSize": 14,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "terraform fmt\nterraform validate\nterraform plan -var-file=\"envs/production.tfvars\"\nterraform apply -var-file=\"envs/production.tfvars\"\n\naws eks update-kubeconfig --name dvn-workshop-production --region us-east-1\nkubectl get nodes\nkubectl get pods -n argocd\nkubectl get application dvn-workshop -n argocd\n\nGitOps: push em main -> CI/CD -> ECR -> kustomization.yaml -> ArgoCD sync",
